{
  "text": "The minimum DC required for composite success clinically has still to be established but is suggested to be at least 55% [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . The DC has a maximum possible rate which will not improve when increasing the total energy level of irradiance from the LCUs [CITATION_3] and will never be 100% [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] .",
  "correct_citation": {
